<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Crystal Palace have asked about Fluminense forward Evanilson, 20, and are monitoring developments with Jeremie Boga the former Chelsea winger now at Sassuolo. </p>

<p>Evanilson, has also been watched by Liverpool and Manchester City, is open to the move but Fluminense would like him to stay until the end of the Brazilian season. </p>

<p>Boga, 23, is wanted by Palace as a potential replacement for Wilfried Zaha. Boga's club Sassuolo rejected an £18m bid from Rennes last week. </p>

<p>Crystal Palace have enquired about Evanilson, who is on loan at Fluminense from Tombense</p>

<p>Palace are also monitoring former Chelsea winger Jeremie Boga, who plays for Sassuolo</p>

<p>Palace are also considering a new loan move for Chelsea’s Michy Batshuayi. </p>

<p>Batshuayi previously had a loan spell at Palace in 2019, during which he scored six goals in 13 games.</p>

<p>He is set to be sent on loan again having been on the periphery of proceedings at Chelsea last season but will reportedly be offered a new contract first. </p>

<p>Palace are also considering a deal to bring Michy Batshuayi back to the club on loan</p>
